{"tid":2411921,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"公屋抽中強檢，唔去得唔得？","createTime":"2021-02-17T16:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T04:26:11.000Z","uid":358055,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"79c32b52c55d46bdbf9e4875388f45e25fde0ea9","tid":2411921,"uid":358055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:37:28.000Z","msg":"認真問<br />\n平時同女朋友響出面住<br />\n最近一星期都冇番過公屋屋企<br />\n但今日抽中左強檢<br />\n公屋有我名，係咪一定要番去檢？<br />\n有冇人試過唔檢，佢係咪會有房署list搵到你？<br />\n如果我老母落去左去檢，証明個單位已經有人檢左得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n感謝<br />\n<br />\n利申：番通宵更，番公屋一來一回3個鐘，真心唔想特登番去檢"},{"pid":"03cdc625f22587ecda5c72ac9984254c2bd0834d","tid":2411921,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:05:01.000Z","msg":"唔一定要返去驗，去你附近個d檢測中心驗都得"},{"pid":"86d6432b54599c3e12f31d0b558a1e5869db51a3","tid":2411921,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:07:29.000Z","msg":"點解搬出去都唔除名？<br />\n<br />\n無收入唔影響富戶所以唔除？"},{"pid":"db58e987095b14b67e37810eadd62628db4ca328","tid":2411921,"uid":309357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86d6432b54599c3e12f31d0b558a1e5869db51a3","tid":2411921,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:07:29.000Z","msg":"點解搬出去都唔除名？<br />\n<br />\n無收入唔影響富戶所以唔除？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:10:26.000Z","msg":"無啦啦做咩要除名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5485ff70a3d3b9dfc93e3e3df39c0b604c31eee","tid":2411921,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:15:02.000Z","msg":"個通告有寫過幾時至幾時逗留過就要驗，你冇返過去就唔需要驗"},{"pid":"203bb4a2de1ab0f2ed92ef5f42a5171f08db9a33","tid":2411921,"uid":289900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86d6432b54599c3e12f31d0b558a1e5869db51a3","tid":2411921,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"re